# Prisma Schema Changes

Never use `prisma db push` to apply schema changes. Always create a migration.

```bash
# ❌ BAD
pnpm prisma db push

# ✅ GOOD
pnpm prisma migrate dev --name your_migration_name
```

Choose a descriptive migration name that reflects the change (e.g., `add_user_email`, `create_heartbeats_table`).
